Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被请来参加这么丰盛的宴会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个见面礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grad 这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最终还是没能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下意识中我就这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在曼哈顿等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你 请你来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是曼哈顿 但范围也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还没把我的名字告诉她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 虽说还要等我还清了Gandor兄弟的人情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能拯救很多小孩了啊 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是毒电波啊 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据英国圣诞老人说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于手机电波 家庭交流变少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩沉迷于电脑 爸爸在搞外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈出去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭破裂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以我们要阻止它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是对策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们没有变老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~ 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不知道为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们经常再生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得庆祝了啊
